summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Department of Parks and Recreation; authorizing increases in 2001 and 2002 Seattle Aquarium and Woodland Park Zoo fees; amending the 2001-2002 fee schedule for the use of park and recreation facilities established under Ordinance 120168; amending section 18.28.010 of the Seattle Municipal Code in connection therewith; and ratifying and confirming prior acts.
